{"word":"τέταρτος","slug":"τέταρτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τέταρτος</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>fourth</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>quartus</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>τὸ τέταρτον</el>, as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>the fourth time</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>: as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, without <a href='S:Article'>Art.</a>, <i>fourthly</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><el>ἡ τετάρτη</el>: <p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>ἡμέρα</el>), <i>the fourth day</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>μοῖρα</el>), <i>a liquid measure</i> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> our <i>quart)</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}